# ─── Production-risk files: NOT listed here ────────────────────────────────
# package.json, package-lock.json, app.json, eas.json are TRACKED on purpose
# (EAS / build pipeline reads them from git). Listing them here would be a
# no-op since gitignore is bypassed for already-tracked files.
#
# To stop your local edits from being staged accidentally, use skip-worktree
# (per-machine, doesn't propagate):
#   git update-index --skip-worktree frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json frontend/app.json
#   git update-index --skip-worktree SuperAdmin/package.json SuperAdmin/package-lock.json
# Undo with:  git update-index --no-skip-worktree <file>
#
# For machine-specific config, use .env / EXPO_PUBLIC_* overrides.

